## Risks & Mitigations

| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|-----------|--------|------------|
| Multi-day bar positioning breaks grid layout | Medium | High | Use CSS Grid `grid-column: span N` instead of absolute positioning |
| Color replacements break existing themes | Low | Medium | Test both light and dark mode thoroughly |
| List view issue is deeper than filtering | Medium | Medium | Add extensive debug logging, investigate event expansion |
| Multi-day bars overlap with day numbers | Medium | Low | Add top padding to bars, adjust vertical positioning |
| Performance issues with many multi-day events | Low | Low | Use useMemo for bar calculations, limit re-renders |

